name: Effluesense: Wildflowers
description:
Eli Joteva
Effluesense: Wildflowers, 2018
JPG
1500x1000 PX, 300dpi 


Is it possible that biological life has senses, desires and pulsations beyond human comprehension? This photography project considers the agency and livelihood of organic materials and ecological terrains. Inspired by theories in vibrant materialism and quantum mechanics, the artist scans various landscapes and organic compositions with gestural laser-light movements in order to expose a fluctuating dimension of plant life.
